title: Devta
subTitle: An ordinary taxi driver becomes part of a notorious gang through a twist of fate and takes on the role of a terrifying assassin.

title: Satya
subTitle: Satya gets acquainted with Bhiku Mhatre, an underworld boss, while serving a term in jail and joins his gang. When he falls in love with Vidya, he is forced to choose between his job and his love.

title: Hiraasat
subTitle: An honest policeman who lives with his wife and a brother who is a student, gets implicated and arrested in a case of drug-trafficking.

title: Khel Khilari Ka
subTitle: Ajit swears revenge after witnessing his family's murder by three thugs. Years later, he becomes a wealthy crime lord, but he still thirsts for revenge.

title: Kahani Kismat Ki
subTitle: After his release from jail, a criminal tries to make an honest living. However, his plans go awry when a woman claims that he is her husband and later he is arrested for murder.

title: Daraar
subTitle: Raj Malhotra, a wealthy man, falls for Priya. However, things get complicated when Vikram, Priya's abusive husband, enters the frame.

title: Naseeb
subTitle: The lives of friends Namdev, Raghu, Damu and Jaggi take a turn for the worse when they win a lottery. Raghu and Damu murder Jaggi and frame Namdev who later returns to seek revenge.

title: Zakhmi Aurat
subTitle: Determined to exact revenge on the goons who gangraped her, Inspector Kiran Dutt, takes matters into her own hands as the law fails to give her justice.

title: Shehzaade
subTitle: Suraj, a justice-loving man, must face a series of obstacles when he discovers his widowed mother's affair with a former prisoner.

title: Shehzaade
subTitle: Suraj, a justice-loving man, must face a series of obstacles when he discovers his widowed mother's affair with a former prisoner.

title: Aulad
subTitle: Believing his wife to be dead, Anand gives up his own child to Yashoda, who has lost her husband and her baby. However, he faces a dilemma when his wife returns.

title: Kaun Kare Kurbanie
subTitle: Arjun Singh, a police inspector, lives peacefully with his family in Mumbai, until an alarming case of harassment and murder turns his life upside down.

title: 16 December
subTitle: Four IRS officers race against the clock to disarm the nuclear bomb planted by a rebel Pakistani terrorist in New Delhi.

title: Keemat
subTitle: After two thugs accidentally kill a man, they hide the truth from his family and try to save his village from the torments of an evil landlord in order to redeem themselves.

title: Dhadkan
subTitle: Anjali and Dev's love story faces a harsh twist when Anjali is forced to marry Ram. Years later, Dev returns to rekindle their romance, only to find that Anjali has grown to love her husband.

title: Shakti: The Power
subTitle: Nandini and Shekhar's visit to India turns tragic when they meet his violent family. After losing Shekhar, Nandini fights to save their son and escape back home.

title: Lal Baadshah
subTitle: Lal Singh, a righteous and helpful man, clashes against Dayal Singh, a powerful personality. However, things get complicated when a hidden treasure is involved and Lal's tragic past is disclosed.

title: Viduthalai Part 1
subTitle: A newly appointed police inspector finds himself in an ethical quandary when he is tasked with hunting down the leader of a fearsome separatist group.

title: Viduthalai Part 1
subTitle: A newly appointed police inspector finds himself in an ethical quandary when he is tasked with hunting down the leader of a fearsome separatist group.

title: Jaane Jigar
subTitle: Two identical women who hail from different backgrounds fall in love with two best friends, Ravi and Vijay. Misunderstandings arise when Ravi and Vijay believe they are in love with the same girl.

title: Ram Balram
subTitle: Unaware of his evil intentions and his role in killing their parents, two brothers Ram and Balram fall victim to their deceitful uncle. They must unite to foil his plans of gaining wealth.

title: Hatya: The Murder
subTitle: Ravi's father, Ratan, gets killed when he refuses to sell his land to Murugan, a wealthy businessman. Later, Ravi sets out to avenge the death of his father.

title: Sultanat
subTitle: Sultan, a brave warrior, tries to win the affections of Yasmin, a beautiful woman. However, his life turns upside down when his father is killed by a general, whom he swears revenge against.

title: Majaal
subTitle: Vijay Kumar, an orphan, is brought up by an advocate. While he falls in love with his daughter and marries her, he struggles to cope with the humiliation he faces from her family.

title: Dil Hi to Hai
subTitle: Twin brothers swap identities in childhood, unknowingly setting the stage for emotional turmoil, romantic confusion, and conflicts tied to their royal lineage.

title: Divya Shakti
subTitle: A young reporter, Prashant Verma, tired of injustice, bears witness to a murder case and wages war against Tau. But in the process, his life and family members get threatened.

title: Ajab Gazabb Love
subTitle: Rajveer, a rich man, falls in love with Madhuri. However, he soon realises that she detests affluent people and in order to win her heart, he, along with his family, pretends to be poor.
